title: Aurelie's Health and Lifestyle Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Salad bar, Juice bar, Take-out, European
description: Vegetarian cafe with a Mediterranean vibe. Offers dishes with tofu, non-dairy cheese, falafel, veggie sausages, and burger patties. Drinks include coffee, veggie juices, and superfood smoothies. Has gluten free baked goods. A retail sells home accessories, health supplements, kitchen consumables, children's lunch boxes, and more. Venue hire is possible. Free Wi-Fi.
